375
00:24:30,202 --> 00:24:31,828
- I'm not gonna...
- She warned me.

376
00:24:31,829 --> 00:24:35,264
I'm not gonna take my book out.
I'm just asking you.

377
00:24:35,291 --> 00:24:38,918
Well, the scuttlebutt for a while
was that he was investigating Kennedy.

378
00:24:38,919 --> 00:24:40,462
Why?

379
00:24:40,463 --> 00:24:44,565
The White House was real paranoid
about Teddy Kennedy.

380
00:24:45,092 --> 00:24:48,511
I remember seeing a book
about Chappaquiddick on his desk.

381
00:24:48,512 --> 00:24:50,221
He was always getting material...

382
00:24:50,222 --> 00:24:53,349
...out of the White House library
