If the story's all right, you'll be on
the phone after I get to 10, all right?

1932
01:59:38,739 --> 01:59:40,489
- Hang up, right?
- That's right.

1933
01:59:40,490 --> 01:59:41,699
- You got it?
- Yeah.

1934
01:59:41,700 --> 01:59:44,994
