1935
01:59:44,995 --> 01:59:46,245
- We all right?
- Yeah.

1936
01:59:46,246 --> 01:59:47,455
Okay, I'm counting.

1937
01:59:47,456 --> 01:59:51,250
One, two, three...

1938
01:59:51,251 --> 01:59:55,463
