1947
02:00:26,119 --> 02:00:27,369
- He confirm?
- Absolutely.

1948
02:00:27,370 --> 02:00:29,472
We gotta tell Bradlee.

1949
02:00:29,956 --> 02:00:33,802
The New York Times
had three columns on it.

1950
