02:11:38,207 --> 02:11:40,876
- Sloan would've told the grand jury.
- Sloan wanted to.

2080
02:11:40,877 --> 02:11:43,362
- Why didn't he?
- Because nobody asked.

2081
02:11:43,796 --> 02:11:46,173
The cover-up had little to do
with the break-in.

2082
02:11:46,174 --> 02:11:48,300
It was to protect covert operations...

2083
02:11:48,301 --> 02:11:50,886
...involving the entire
U.S. intelligence community.

2084
02:11:50,887 --> 02:11:53,555
Did Deep Throat say
that people's lives are in danger?

2085
02:11:53,556 --> 02:11:57,017
- Yes.
- What else did he say?

2086
02:11:57,018 --> 02:11:59,992
He said everyone is involved.

2087
02:12:06,486 --> 02:12:09,237
You know the results
of the latest Gallup poll?

2088
02:12:09,238 --> 02:12:12,073
Half the country never even heard
of the word "Watergate."

2089
02:12:12,074 --> 02:12:14,535
Nobody gives a shit.

2090
02:12:16,370 --> 02:12:19,088
You guys are probably pretty tired, right?

2091
02:12:19,373 --> 02:12:22,292
Well, you should be. Go on home.

2092
02:12:22,293 --> 02:12:25,587
Get a nice hot bath, rest up 15 minutes...

2093
02:12:25,588 --> 02:12:28,423
...then get your asses back in gear.

2094
02:12:28,424 --> 02:12:32,527
We're under a lot of pressure, you know,
and you put us there.

2095
02:12:33,596 --> 02:12:35,013
Nothing's riding on this...

2096
02:12:35,014 --> 02:12:38,183
...except the First Amendment
of the Constitution...

2097
02:12:38,184 --> 02:12:42,984
...freedom of the press,
and maybe the future of the country.

2098
02:12:43,940 --> 02:12:46,274
Not that any of that matters...

2099
02:12:46,275 --> 02:12:50,737
...but if you guys fuck up again,
I'm gonna get mad.

2100
02:12:51,697 --> 02:12:53,645
Good night.

2101
02:13:20,677 --> 02:13:22,710
Now, fellow Americans...

2102
02:13:22,711 --> 02:13:27,111
...the honorable chief justice
will administer the oath of office...

2103
02:13:27,942 --> 02:13:31,152
...to the president
of the United States of America.

2104
02:13:31,153 --> 02:13:33,488
Mr. Chief Justice.

2105
02:13:54,844 --> 02:13:59,097
Mr. President, are you ready
to take the constitutional oath?

2106
02:13:59,098 --> 02:14:03,518
If you will place your left hand
on the Bible and raise your right hand...

2107
02:14:03,519 --> 02:14:05,270
...and please repeat after me:

2108
02:14:05,271 --> 02:14:08,565
I, Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...

2109
02:14:08,566 --> 02:14:10,942
I, Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...

2110
02:14:10,943 --> 02:14:15,543
...that I will faithfully execute
the office of president of the United States...

2111
02:14:15,665 --> 02:14:19,801
...that I will faithfully execute the
office of president of the United States...

2112
02:14:19,802 --> 02:14:22,362
...and will, to the best of my ability...

2113
02:14:22,463 --> 02:14:24,606
...and will, to the best of my ability...

2114
02:14:24,607 --> 02:14:26,908
...preserve, protect and defend...

2115
02:14:26,909 --> 02:14:29,210
...the Constitution of the United States...

2116
02:14:29,211 --> 02:14:33,181
...preserve and protect and defend
the Constitution of the United States...

2117
02:14:33,182 --> 02:14:34,883
CHIEF JUSTICE.
...so help me God.

2118
02:14:34,884 --> 02:14:37,601
...so help me God.
